                    <div class="space-y-4 md:w-1/3">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center rounded text-white font-bold tracking-widest">MH</div>
                            <h2 class="text-[1.3rem] font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Mundo homeopático</h2>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-[13px] text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-light md:pr-4">Más de 20 años formulando soluciones magistrales con absoluta precisión y los más altos estándares de calidad internacional.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-4 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left md:w-1/3">
                        <div class="h-10 flex items-center"><h3 class="text-[13px] font-bold text-slate-300 tracking-[0.1em]">Síguenos</h3></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-start gap-4">
                            <!-- Instagram -->
                            <a href="#/" class="w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-800 text-slate-400 hover:bg-pink-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 group" aria-label="Instagram">
