                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-3 flex flex-col h-full md:items-end md:text-right md:w-1/3">
                        <div class="h-10 flex items-center"><p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-300">© 2026 Mundo Homeopático.</p></div>
                        <div class="mt-1 space-y-1">
                            <p class="text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500">Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
                            <p class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 font-medium">Medellín, Colombia</p>
                            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jalfredopabon/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block text-[12px] text-slate-500 font-medium hover:text-white transition-colors group">Creado por <span class="text-slate-300 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">Alfredo Pabón</span></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
